This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category of cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with natural language processing and semantic parsing. The paper also mentions the use of contextualized embeddings, which is a popular technique in the field of NLP. Additionally, the paper may also belong to the sub-categories of cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as the techniques used in the paper involve machine learning algorithms. The sub-categories of cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) and cs.SD (Software Engineering) are less likely but still possible as the paper deals with neural network models and software engineering aspects of error analysis.
